(190, 264, 'Central Market - Bantama, Kumasi', 'Kumasi, the capital of Ghanaâ€™s Ashanti region, was named the Garden City of West Africa by the then colonial head of the Gold Coast. Kumasi also happens to be the seat of the Asante monarchy, whose head is the Asantehene â€“ Otumfuo Osei Tutu II. The As', 3055, '2012-12-02 19:36:12', '2012-12-02 19:36:12', 1),
