(553, '1238969156', 'Monkey', '1238969156.jpg', 'The spiritual belief attached to the monkey sacred grove by the people of Duasidan Community in Dorman District of the Brong Ahafo region of Ghana has given a special status to their monkey sanctuary.', NULL, 255, '2009-04-05 20:52:45', '2009-04-05 20:52:45', '968d139c8a89d54ac3f06fb287e91b249a644ed9', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
(554, '1238969280', 'Monkey', '1238969280.jpg', 'There is no legal protection (legislative instrument), as such are faced with related erosion of traditional values, agricultural expansion, demographic changes and religious growth. The hitherto traditional belief and practice that acted as effective control in protection the sacred grove is now being overwhelmed by these changes.', NULL, 421, '2009-04-05 20:52:45', '2009-04-05 20:52:45', '968d139c8a89d54ac3f06fb287e91b249a644ed9', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
(555, '1238969358', 'Funeral for the Monkeys', '1238969358.jpg', 'Due to this spiritual nature, economic role, health support of this monkeys. Burial and funerals are normally preformed for the death of any monkeys.In the same vein the birth and death of any community member, the monkeys are accordingly informed through the pouring of libation and other sacrifices. ', NULL, 274, '2009-04-05 20:52:45', '2009-04-05 20:52:45', '968d139c8a89d54ac3f06fb287e91b249a644ed9', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
