(566, '1239236340', 'Antelope', '1239236340.jpg', 'The 4840 square kilometers large Park is home to some 100 mammal species and 300 bird species. The mammals include elephants, leopards, various types of antelopes, buffaloes, hyenas, monkeys and warthogs. There are approximately 600 km of game viewing roads in Mole.', NULL, 263, '2009-04-09 00:06:18', '2009-04-09 00:06:18', '968d139c8a89d54ac3f06fb287e91b249a644ed9', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
