(643, '1240178865', 'Fresh beans', '1240178865.jpg', 'Cocoa beans are planted in this state, when they are fresh like this, never try planting the dry beans, all chocolate lovers it will only rot in the soil.Cocoa pods can keep the beans fresh for 3months.', NULL, 335, '2009-04-19 21:03:55', '2009-04-19 21:03:55', '968d139c8a89d54ac3f06fb287e91b249a644ed9', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
(644, '1240179051', 'Cocoa Tree', '1240179051.jpg', 'The cocoa plants are low trees of the genus Theobroma cacao L., with fruit pods 20-30cm long (right), which are yellow or red in colour when mature. They contain a mildly sweet white pulp and many flat seeds, oil from which is used in cosmetics and perfume. The pulp is the source of chocolate and cocoa butter. There are 22 varieties of cocoa, categorized by the colour and shape of pods and their chemical makeup.', NULL, 356, '2009-04-19 21:03:55', '2009-04-19 21:03:55', '968d139c8a89d54ac3f06fb287e91b249a644ed9', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
(645, '1240179220', 'Tetteh Quarshie Memorial Hospital', '1240179220.jpg', 'Tetteh Quarshie Memorial Hospital, this is some 15 minutes walk from the Farm and is also situated at Mampong-Akuapim ', NULL, 529, '2009-04-19 21:03:55', '2009-04-19 21:03:55', '968d139c8a89d54ac3f06fb287e91b249a644ed9', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
