(872, '1242865380', 'Cyborg The Welder', '1242865380.jpg', 'Cyborg as he is popularly known at La, was born Benjamin Lartey and he''s by far the best welder in Ghana. He has put in about months of work, including an engine rebuild which he prefers to put infront of the car rather than the back as it is with VW Beetle. He also welds and moulds car parts which are very difficult to find on the market. His workshop is located at La near the Mawuli restaurant. Call now +233 21 764888.', NULL, 383, '2009-05-20 22:29:51', '2009-05-20 22:29:51', '968d139c8a89d54ac3f06fb287e91b249a644ed9', 20, 5, 1, NULL),
