(1059, '1244982371', 'Villa Cisneros Resort Sogakope', '1244982371.jpg', 'VillaExperience the Ghanaian culture at its best. Our resident brass-band or traditional musical performances by local agbadza and Borborbor troupes, form the basis of entertainment at Villa Cisneros Resort. Numerous sculpture gardens with man-made fountains depict the scenic beauty and rich Ghanaian (Ewe) culture.Cisneros Resort Sogakope', NULL, 1288, '2009-06-14 11:32:32', '2009-06-14 11:32:32', '968d139c8a89d54ac3f06fb287e91b249a644ed9', 4, 1, 1, NULL),
