(1061, '1244982478', 'Boat Cruise', '1244982478.jpg', 'Enjoy a cruise on the volta lake, cruising by speedboat, traditional dug out canoe, BSI luxury boat or a 250 seater liner; swim in our semi-olympic size pool, lawn and table tennis and a wide variety of indoor games all at your disposal. You could also go biking , sports , fishing or bird watching. It is our pleasure to provide leisure.', NULL, 608, '2009-06-14 11:32:32', '2009-06-14 11:32:32', '968d139c8a89d54ac3f06fb287e91b249a644ed9', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
