(1064, '1244982814', 'Infra Red Sauna and a Jacuzzi bath', '1244982814.jpg', 'SPA is an abbreviation for the Latin phrase Sanus Per Aqua which means â€œHealth Through waterâ€?. A SPA is a centre for scientific relaxation and rejuvenation which helps to promote wellness and better health conditions. Basically it is a water treatment process', NULL, 612, '2009-06-14 11:32:32', '2009-06-14 11:32:32', '968d139c8a89d54ac3f06fb287e91b249a644ed9', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
