(1066, '1244983205', 'Swimming Pool', '1244983205.jpg', 'Enjoy having fun cruising by speedboat, traditional dug out canoe, BSI luxury boat or a 250 seater liner; swim in our semi-olympic size pool, lawn and table tennis and a wide variety of indoor games all at your disposal. You could also go biking , sports , fishing or bird watching. It is our pleasure to provide leisure. Come to us for a perfectly relaxing vacation', NULL, 699, '2009-06-14 11:32:32', '2009-06-14 11:32:32', '968d139c8a89d54ac3f06fb287e91b249a644ed9', 16, 4, 1, NULL),
(1067, '1244983488', 'Villa Cisneros Resort Sogakope', '1244983488.jpg', 'Looking for one of the most beautiful riural settings Ghana can boast of? We have it, Located at the eastern bank of the Volta, Ghana''s longest river, about 14 kilometres from the sea, on a 20 hectre estate at Sogakope in the Volta Region.... You''ll find Villa Cisneros.The Gateway to Ghana''s Rural Beauty. Lying midway between two West African Cities of Accra (Ghana) and Lome (Togo), it is within an hour''s drive on asphalted road from each city.\r\nTel: +233 249795098, +233 277850326 or +233 244330624\r\ncisnerosvilla2@yahoo.com www.villacisnerosresort.com\r\n', NULL, 1372, '2009-06-14 11:32:32', '2009-06-14 11:32:32', '968d139c8a89d54ac3f06fb287e91b249a644ed9', 12, 3, 1, NULL),
