(1594, '1251347041', 'Keta Sea Defence', '1251347041.jpg', 'Keta is a city in Volta Region, Ghana. It was an important trading post between the 14th and late 20th century via a port and fort built by the Dutch in 1784. Parts of the city were devastated by sea erosion between the 1960s and 1980s. There was a massive sea defence project few years ago, thus halting the disturbances of the sea.', NULL, 947, '2009-08-27 04:04:57', '2009-08-27 04:04:57', '968d139c8a89d54ac3f06fb287e91b249a644ed9', 8, 2, 1, NULL),
