(1668, '1253462399', 'W.E.B Du Bios and Kwame Nkrumah', '1253462399.JPG', 'Du Bois was invited to Ghana in 1961 by President Kwame Nkrumah to direct the Encyclopedia Africana, a government production, and a long-held dream of his. When, in 1963, he was refused a new U.S. passport, he and his wife, Shirley Graham Du Bois, became citizens of Ghana.', NULL, 464, '2009-09-20 15:42:27', '2009-09-20 15:42:27', '968d139c8a89d54ac3f06fb287e91b249a644ed9', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
