(1971, '1269198681', 'Complex', '1269198681.jpg', 'Sicut Miles Christi : (The Latin word for As a Soldier of Christ) is the motto of the school. \r\n\r\nIn Bishop Augustine Herman''s lifetime his personal motto was St Paul''s words - SICUT MILES CHRISTI - which in English means AS A SOLDIER OF CHRIST. This has remained the motto of the College too.\r\n\r\nBishop Augustine Herman''s wondrous deeds remain within the hearts and minds of the many faithful he converted to the Catholic faith in the Keta Diocese (now divided into two Dioceses, namely, Keta-Akatsi, Ho and Jasikan)', NULL, 1749, '2010-03-21 18:55:07', '2010-03-21 18:55:07', '968d139c8a89d54ac3f06fb287e91b249a644ed9', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
(1972, '1269198713', 'Dinning Hall', '1269198713.jpg', 'Come join with us to sing\r\nIn praise of BIHECO\r\nWhere God and Light we seek\r\nIn spirit bold and free\r\nHail BIHECO,\r\nHail BIHECO, \r\nHail BIHECO\r\nMater, Mater Alma \r\nThy loving children true \r\nAll rally ''neath thy sail\r\nAnd pledge as loyal crew\r\nTo live and die for thee\r\nHail BIHECO, \r\nHail BIHECO, \r\nHail BIHECO\r\nMater, Mater Alma\r\n\r\n\r\nThe School Anthem was Composed by:\r\nE. Y. Egblewogbe\r\nSnr. Prefect 1957\r\n\r\n ', NULL, 2205, '2010-03-21 18:55:07', '2010-03-21 18:55:07', '968d139c8a89d54ac3f06fb287e91b249a644ed9', 10, 3, 1, NULL),
(1973, '1269198763', 'Administration Block', '1269198763.jpg', 'The ORGANISING COMMITTEE of Bishop Herman''s 60th anniversary is calling on  Past and Present BEHICANS to participate and cooperate fully in the preparation(s) towards the anniversary in 2012.\r\n\r\nCONTACT THE SECRETARIAT FOR MORE DETAILS\r\n\r\n Secretariat Address: The Secretariat Bishop Herman Old Boys'' Union F652 / 2B Mission Street Extension Osu-RE, Accra\r\n Postal Address P.O. Box AN 15445 Accra-North Ghana. West Africa \r\n\r\nPhone: +233-21-240287 Fax: +233-21-240288 \r\n\r\nEmail: info@bhobu.org\r\n\r\nPLEASE PASS THIS MESSAGE TO ANY BIHECAN YOU KNOW\r\n\r\nTHANKS', NULL, 2552, '2010-03-21 18:55:07', '2010-03-21 18:55:07', '968d139c8a89d54ac3f06fb287e91b249a644ed9', 8, 3, 1, NULL),
(1974, '1269198848', 'Bishop Herman College--- www.bhobu.org', '1269198848.jpg', 'Bishop Herman College was founded on February 28, 1952 at Kpando in the Volta Region of Ghana by the then Keta Diocese of the Catholic Church as a boy''s Secondary Boarding school.\r\n\r\nBIHECO as the school has come to be known, was named after Bishop Augustine Herman, a Frenchman who was Bishop of the Keta Diocese from 1923-1945. Bishop Herman''s legendary exemplary Christian life and his love for education saw him setting up schools in most of the communities he succeeded in planting the Catholic faith. It came thus as no surprise that when the Keta Diocese wanted to establish an exemplary, par excellence secondary school to train young boys in the pursuit of spiritual and academic discipline they decided to name it after him.\r\nThe Secretariat\r\nBishop Herman Old Boys'' Union\r\nF652 / 2B \r\nMission Street Extension\r\nOsu-RE, Accra \r\nPostal Address \r\nP.O. Box AN 15445 \r\nAccra-North \r\nGhana. West Africa\r\nPhone: +233-21-240287\r\nFax: +233-21-240288 \r\nEmail: info@bhobu.org', NULL, 10937, '2010-03-21 18:55:07', '2010-03-21 18:55:07', '968d139c8a89d54ac3f06fb287e91b249a644ed9', 15, 7, 1, NULL),
