(1997, '1271267864', 'My Photo Story', '1271267864.jpg', 'I have spent so many years in London but one can never compare it with the months I''ve spent here in Ghana. I have relocated back to my roots and I''m so in love with this friendly and safe country. Indeed there is no place like home. Irrespective of my busy schedule at work, I make time out to chill. I love every minute here in Ghana, cruising from one end of this lovely nation to the other. Don''t let me even start with those fabulous weekends filled with excitement from one joint to the other. Well if you want to know more about me, do continue reading my photo story. Hi everyone, I''m Nana Yaa.', NULL, 813, '2010-04-14 16:59:43', '2010-04-14 16:59:43', '968d139c8a89d54ac3f06fb287e91b249a644ed9', 1, 1, 1, NULL),
