(2081, '1278333385', 'Entrance Addo Elephant National Park', '1278333385.jpg', 'Several historic sites can be found in the area which date back as far as 1829. The most well known site is the Drift House, the Inn used by most people crossing the Addo drift from the old Cape Colony into the Hinterland. ', '', 364, '2010-07-05 12:36:25', '2010-07-05 12:36:25', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
