(2100, '1279498247', 'Traffic', '1279498247.jpg', 'I guess this picture virtually speaks for itself.  I would be stuck in this intolerable traffic jam if I had boarded a cab.  And worse would be inhaling fumes from the exhaust pipes of all these cars.  No wonder we are always getting sick.  This is just pure air pollution.  Phewwwww, thank God for the train.', NULL, 455, '2010-07-19 00:10:47', '2010-07-19 00:10:47', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
(2101, '1279498363', 'Ama, enjoying her Novel', '1279498363.jpg', 'This novel is so interesting that I canâ€™t put this book down, itâ€™s totally addictive.  Iâ€™m feeling so relaxed because the seats in this train is so comfortable.  Well mokocharlie fans Iâ€™m about to reach my destination.  And this is the part where I say thank you for reading my photo story.\r\nChoa!\r\n', NULL, 417, '2010-07-19 00:12:43', '2010-07-19 00:12:43', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
(2102, '1279498650', 'Ama buys an ice-cream to cool down', '1279498650.jpg', 'The one thing I enjoy about train rides are the stations.  At each stop you can get refreshments sold to you by hawkers.  You can get anything from ice-cream to cakes.  And as you cans see Iâ€™m getting myself some ice-cream to cool down.  Another interesting thing Iâ€™ve noticed is hawkers by the train stations donâ€™t harass you like the ones on the streets.  So I always get the opportunity to buy without any influence.', NULL, 440, '2010-07-19 00:17:30', '2010-07-19 00:17:30', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
(2103, '1279498977', 'Reading', '1279498977.jpg', 'Have you realized that itâ€™s virtually impossible to concentrate while reading in a noisy environment?  Well, try riding the train and you will see the difference.  You will surely have all the peace and serenity you need to enjoy a good novel', NULL, 435, '2010-07-19 00:22:57', '2010-07-19 00:22:57', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
(2104, '1279499043', 'Aloneness ', '1279499043.jpg', 'Most people are not used to using the train down here, so itâ€™s mostly empty.  That can only mean one thing, a lonely ride.  However if youâ€™re like me and enjoy peace and quiet then you will love the ride.  Itâ€™s a perfect time and place to recollect on a dayâ€™s work.', NULL, 462, '2010-07-19 00:24:03', '2010-07-19 00:24:03', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
(2105, '1279499244', 'Stop', '1279499244.jpg', 'I guess this picture virtually speaks for itself.  I would be stuck in this intolerable traffic jam if I had boarded a cab.  And worse would be inhaling fumes from the exhaust pipes of all these cars.  No wonder we are always getting sick.  This is just pure air pollution.  Phewwwww, thank God for the train.', NULL, 545, '2010-07-19 00:27:24', '2010-07-19 00:27:24', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
(2106, '1279501919', 'My Photo Story 3 : Ama tells her story', '1279501919.jpg', ' A lady in subtle formal pink, this can only mean one thing, Iâ€™m a working class woman.  Hi guys my name is Ama.  Life in Ghana can really be frustrating especially when you work in a reputable company like me and cannot afford to be late.  How does one avert this absurd traffic congestion?  Well I will tell you how, by using the rail form of transportation.  I donâ€™t have time to be stuck in traffic for long hours as my family totally depends on me, since I do all the cooking at home.  And thatâ€™s why I love using the train; Iâ€™m totally guaranteed to reach home on time.  Keep on reading mokocharlie fans and I will show you how I beat the traffic everydayâ€¦', 'COMG1ZWU3Zs', 874, '2010-07-19 01:11:59', '2010-07-19 01:11:59', 'admin', 15, 3, 1, NULL),
(2107, '1279501840', 'My Photo Story: Aloneness', '1279501840.jpg', 'Most people are not used to using the train down here, so itâ€™s mostly empty.  That can only mean one thing, a lonely ride.  However if youâ€™re like me and enjoy peace and quiet then you will love the ride.  Itâ€™s a perfect time and place to recollect on a dayâ€™s work. This train runs Sakumono and Accra and this is how it''s first class looks like. It has a well designed leather seat which is very comfortable to make one enjoy the ride.', '', 778, '2010-07-19 01:10:40', '2010-07-19 01:10:40', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
(2108, '1279501226', 'My Photo Story: Ama enters the train', '1279501226.jpg', 'One must be careful when climbing the steps to the train, it can be very tricky. On getting here early, one is able to find a good seat in the First class coach. The second class is usually crowded. And it''s 60pesewas for First class and 50pesewas for the second class', '', 566, '2010-07-19 01:00:26', '2010-07-19 01:00:26', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
(2109, '1279501132', 'Old Folk', '1279501132.jpg', 'The old folks also prefer the train to Cabs and the Trotros just for the same reason...Traffic!', NULL, 701, '2010-07-19 00:58:52', '2010-07-19 00:58:52', 'admin', 5, 1, 1, NULL),
(2110, '1279501711', 'My Photo Story: Aloneness', '1279501711.jpg', 'A train ride is so comfortable.  Unlike a car whereby you get tossed left and right each time the car turns.  I mean one can do some work in peace and comfort without having to worry about holding their laptops tight every second.  If you have a deadline you can be sure to complete it well before you reach work so you donâ€™t get fired.  Trains can sure be life savers!', NULL, 679, '2010-07-19 01:08:31', '2010-07-19 01:08:31', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
(2111, '1279500845', 'Train', '1279500845.jpg', 'Sometimes, even if the train is not full to capacity others prefer to stand', 'COMG1ZWU3Zs', 606, '2010-07-19 00:54:05', '2010-07-19 00:54:05', 'admin', 5, 1, 1, NULL),
