(2144, '1280708478', 'MPLAZA HOTEL', '1280708478.jpg', 'Ghana''s only exclusive hotel, and the nation''s hotel for presidents and royals.\nRecognized for providing the tightest in guest security, privacy, personalized\nservices and convenience in doing business from the comfort of one''s hotel\nroom. Mplaza Hotel, the ultimate in exclusive services. Our niche clientele features diplomats, corperate chief executives and celebreties in both sports and entertainment. Besides the gallery of personalities we have hosted, our ranking status in hosting of conferences, high profile banquets, receptions, very private events like honeymooning is second to none. \nTEL:(233-21) 763 417 - 9/ 763 492 - 5/ 775 922 ', '', 350, '2010-08-02 00:21:18', '2010-08-02 00:21:18', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, NULL);
