(2146, '1280708963', 'Swimming at MPLAZA HOTEL', '1280708963.jpg', 'After working hard all week, this is how i love to cool off at the weekend. Relaxing in this cool clean swimming pool at Mplaza Hotel is extremely refreshing and helps me cut down stress. It''s usually not packed here and the rate is very reasonable too. Please join me this weekend. YOU''LL LOVE IT!!!!', 'fXs-h0Awapw', 571, '2010-08-02 00:29:23', '2010-08-02 00:29:23', 'admin', 5, 1, 1, NULL),
