(2354, '1289111031', 'Bojo Beach Resort', '1289111031.jpg', 'The Bojo White Sand Beach is the latest addition to the beach party situation arising along Ghana''s 540Km pristine beach line. Situated next to the Densu delta Ramsar site and along the Atlantic Ocean, in its uniqueness and lovely blend of Caribbean and Ghanaian cultural architecture is the inviting Bojo beach.', '', 627, '2010-11-07 06:23:51', '2010-11-07 06:23:51', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
