(2356, '1289111153', 'Island Bojo Beach Resort', '1289111153.jpg', 'The beach area is another kind of island situated between the canal and the sea right on a stretch of sand bar. The sand bar has so much to offer that will surprise you. To get to the sand bar, you will have to cruise either by the Bojo Cruiser or a canoe over one of the Densu distributaries.', '', 1157, '2010-11-07 06:25:53', '2010-11-07 06:25:53', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
