(2378, '1291156663', 'Harbin Entertainment Centre', '1291156663.jpg', 'Join the Bowling Club at Harbin Entertainment Centre on the Accra-tema road. The centre comes along with the first bowling game facilities in Ghana. It is fully equipped with the state-of-the-art equipment for this physical endurance and highly entertaining game in which heavy balls are rolled along a special track towards a group of wooden pins. It''s located next door to the Next Door Beach Resort.', '', 2127, '2010-11-30 22:37:43', '2010-11-30 22:37:43', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
