(2380, '1291157332', 'Rockstoneâ€™s Office', '1291157332.jpg', 'After enjoying enormous success in the entertainment industry as one of the greatest rappers of all time and the forerunner of the genre â€œHipLifeâ€, Reggie now takes a new turn as the CEO of Rockstoneâ€™s Office formerly known as Office Night club. This hangout is a blend of club and pub so he terms it â€œPLUBâ€. PLUB is a self coined word from Pub and Club used by Reggie to define his new hangout in the heart of the business city of Accra. Rockstone''s Office is behind the Police Headquarters at Cantonments, Accra.', '', 1015, '2010-11-30 22:48:52', '2010-11-30 22:48:52', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
(2381, '1291157490', 'Stone Lodge ', '1291157490.jpg', 'Situated about 67 kilometres from Accra on the road to Asutsuare and near impressive Shai Hills, Stone Lodge is a tranquil development of residential chalets, organic farms, entertainment and sporting facilities for the whole family. Visit us to spend a comfortable and relaxing time surrounded by nature but with all the luxuries of the city. You will have access to our bars, excellent restaurant, golf course, squash court, riding and hiking trails.Tel:  233 208292311, 233 208292311/  233 208292268, 233 208292268,  Fax: 233244 303901. email:info@stonelodge.biz www.stonelodge.biz', '', 1805, '2010-11-30 22:51:30', '2010-11-30 22:51:30', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
