(2385, '1294642120', 'Making Palm oil', '1294642120.jpg', 'After the oil is squeezed out, the roughage is removed from the squeezer and dried.  After which it is sorted for palm kernels which is found inside the palm fruits.  Oil can also be extracted from the kernels also.  This is called palm kernel oil.  However I will end it here, how to extract oil from the kernels will be another dayâ€™s events.  Hope you enjoyed my photo story.  Cheers!', '', 478, '2011-01-10 06:48:40', '2011-01-10 06:48:40', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
(2386, '1294642196', 'Palm oil', '1294642196.jpg', 'I personally enjoyed this part.  This is the time for the strongest of men to display their power.  As simple as this may seem it requires brute power in order to turn the handle of the squeezer which extracts the oil as you can see it dripping.  This is done continuously until the oil ceases to come.  The oil is then distilled and after which you will see that it is red in colour.   This is so because of its high beta-carotene content.   Palm oil can be used for cooking and so many other things.  And there we are, our very own palm oil extracted from palm fruits!', '', 456, '2011-01-10 06:49:56', '2011-01-10 06:49:56', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
(2387, '1294642323', 'Palm oil', '1294642323.jpg', 'After the palm fruits have been pounded, they are placed into a metal squeezer which is man operated.  And I would like to congratulate these men because this part is the hardest.  They scoop out the mashed fruits while they are still hot like lava.', '', 427, '2011-01-10 06:52:03', '2011-01-10 06:52:03', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
(2388, '1294642616', 'Palm oil', '1294642616.jpg', 'After the fruits are well cooked, they pound it to get the fruit off the kernel and more hands are needed to complete this task.', '', 438, '2011-01-10 06:56:56', '2011-01-10 06:56:56', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
(2389, '1294642720', 'Palm oil', '1294642720.jpg', 'Here the ripe palm fruits are place in pots and cooked on an open flame for hours till the fruits are soft enough to be mashed.', '', 518, '2011-01-10 06:58:40', '2011-01-10 06:58:40', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
(2390, '1294642862', 'Palm oil', '1294642862.jpg', 'Since the extraction of oil from palm trees is a long process, more hands are always necessary in order to accomplish the end product.  Here I witnessed so many people both men and woman sorting out the palm fruits and selecting the finest to be cooked.\nAs you can see the women have separated their ripe and unripe palm fruits which are now ready to be put in a pot on placed on an open fire and cooked.', '', 553, '2011-01-10 07:01:02', '2011-01-10 07:01:02', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
(2391, '1294642954', 'Making Palm oil', '1294642954.jpg', 'After the palm fruits have been removed from the pulp the fruits are sorted by hand to make sure that the finest are selected for processing.  In so doing they also remove the shrubs and weeds away from the fruits.  The ripe palm fruits produce more oil than the unripe ones.', '', 1070, '2011-01-10 07:02:34', '2011-01-10 07:02:34', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
(2392, '1294643048', 'Making Palm oil', '1294643048.jpg', 'I watched this man with a cutlass cutting into the palm fruit bunches   in an attempt to release the palm fruits which will just fall loosely on the ground gradually.  It is a tedious job and one really needs to be careful else you can mutilate yourself.', '', 654, '2011-01-10 07:04:08', '2011-01-10 07:04:08', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
(2393, '1294643135', 'Making Palm oil', '1294643135.jpg', 'Palm trees are common in Africa, Latin America and parts of Asia.  And it is the highest oil producing tree known to man.   I went for a retreat and just couldnâ€™t help but share with you the process the inhabitants of this land go through in order to get oil.  I must say in as much as its exciting it is also loads of hard work!  And In this photo story I will take you through all the steps taken in order to achieve the end product, palm oilâ€¦ Hi, i''m Kwaku and this is my photo Story', 'PdKmHTcRT_4', 1101, '2011-01-10 07:05:35', '2011-01-10 07:05:35', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
