(2414, '1295985208', 'Boxing in Accra', '1295985208.jpg', 'Boxing Coach Daniel Q. Lartey, owns the FIT SQUARE BOXING CLUB in Kokomlemle just behind the Fâ€™Eden Mission School. He started training boxers as far back as 1986 and won his first title with Adamu Mohamed, who became the National West African Champion that same year. Heâ€™s also trained boxers like Joseph Agbeko, Micheal Arye, Daniel Tetteh , Yakubu Amidu who now currently resides  in the United States  and many more. He started this gym two years ago, and already one of his boxers has won the Pan African Titleâ€¦ First in the history of Ghana.  In addition six boxers he produced who are in the national team are now all going professional. Call  233 277 812860 if you''re interested in becoming a professional boxer.', '', 758, '2011-01-25 19:53:28', '2011-01-25 19:53:28', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
(2415, '1296737329', 'Olumo Rock - Nigeria', '1296737329.jpg', 'It is often helpful to enlist the services of a guide who possess vast knowledge of the history of the rock and the culture of the people. This makes for an interesting climb as every twist and turn will reveal a significant story making the trip a truly memorable one. On the way back down the rock, the sight of the Ogun river running like a silver chain amidst a forest of aged red corrugated roofs bordered by thick green forests which melt into the horizon is breathtaking.', '', 333, '2011-02-03 12:48:49', '2011-02-03 12:48:49', 'admin', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
